description: Returns information about an audience model.

parameters.name: audienceModelArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the audience model that you are interested in.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the audience model was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The most recent time at which the audience model was updated.

nested_items.name: trainingDataStartTime
nested_items.description: The start date specified for the training window.

nested_items.name: trainingDataEndTime
nested_items.description: The end date specified for the training window.

nested_items.name: audienceModelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the audience model.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the audience model.

nested_items.name: trainingDatasetArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the training dataset that was used for this audience model.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the audience model.

nested_items.name: statusDetails
nested_items.description: Details about the status of the audience model.

nested_items.name: statusCode
nested_items.description: The status code that was returned. The status code is intended for programmatic error handling. Clean Rooms ML will not change the status code for existing error conditions.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The error message that was returned. The message is intended for human consumption and can change at any time. Use the statusCode for programmatic error handling.

nested_items.name: kmsKeyArn
nested_items.description: The KMS key ARN used for the audience model.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the audience model.
